 area was fully developed,\\\" the restaurant said in a statement shared with Dished.\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our decade-long presence\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 338}, {\"ngram\": \"this neighbourhood\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 360}, {\"ngram\": \"the first restaurants\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 396}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"the restaurant\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 469}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 489}, {\"ngram\": \"Dished\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Despite our efforts, we could not reach an agreement with the landlord, so we are now searching for a new location.\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 627, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our efforts\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"an agreement\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 564}, {\"ngram\": \"the landlord\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 582}, {\"ngram\": \"a new location\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However,Ophelia, our other establishment, will remain open, so we will still be around to serve our guests and friends in the area.\\\"\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 636, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ophelia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.961345588153218e-17, \"text\": \"Ophelia\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ophelia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ophelia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our other establishment\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"our guests\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You might also like:Wendy's to offer $1 fry deal across Canada for National Fry DayLook Inside: One of Vancouver's most anticipated cocktail concepts opens this weekMusic icons Missy Elliott, B